reviewText: Kept my kids busy throughout a 6 hour car ride
This video is funny, smart and well produced, perfect entertainment for a Jewish girl or boy. My kids watched it a dozen times!
there is not enough material out like this today.  Really wonderful.  Good message, and very high quality.  My four year old is obsessed.
This video is great!  It has catchy songs, good morals and lessons and is illustrated beautifully. the kids (and their mama:) love it!
i bought this video from my young kids and they love it. keep up the good work. we cant wait for another one to come out.
